summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Whitman Avenue from North 59th Street to North 62nd Street, et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 22907, creating Local Improvement District No. 2236 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
